# QuantIQ India — Environment Variables
#
# Market data (NSE + yfinance) requires NO API key.
# The only key you need is Groq for AI features.

# ── AI (required for AI Intel tab) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Free tier at https://console.groq.com — no credit card required
# Model used: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_groq_key_here

# ── Optional overrides ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: http://localhost:8000
# REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
# REACT_APP_WS_URL=ws://localhost:8000
